title: Ahoy! 100% (All 61 Issues) David H Archive
description:
Ahoy! 100% (All 61 Issues) David H. Archive

Also includes the Ahoy! magazine disk collection archive, that has never been released to the C64 community until now (other Ahoy! archives on the internet claim to be 100%, and are close to it, but have some faulty disk images).

Please note there are two Ahoy! 100% archives on the internet, and both are from different archivists and a seperate collection.  As such each collection has it's pros and cons.

Enjoy!
